[b]Sprint #1[/b] covers [b]What is an API?[/b]. This first of three sprints begins on June 19 and concludes on June 25, 2023. There is no certificate for completing this course. Once you complete this unit (approximately one hour) share an update below by clicking "Add a reply" so that I can monitor participant progress. Then, proceed to the next unit in the same video.

